Terms & Conditions
By using the CatchSign app, you accept the following terms
and conditions:
We handle your personal information in a secure manner. You
must provide the necessary personal details to be able to sign
documents. We store your date of birth, name, address, mobile
number and email address in our internal database. This is
personal information you have provided to us, which is
necessary to be able to carry out our obligations to you as a
signatory. We do not share any of your information with third
parties.
When you use CatchSign we will log which operating system
your device uses, your IP address and which geographical area
you are in at the time of signing. All signed documents are
stored in our internal database. These documents are only
available for the core system and via your access on your
device.
Norwegian Exporters needs this app to sign the Norwegian
Catch Certificates.
Fishermen (skippers)/customers connected to one of the five
Norwegian sales organisations needs this app to sign sales-
and landings- notes.
A signed document will consist of your full name, the date and
time and your position (GPS) when you digitally signed your
document.
